Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}站住 站住 快快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是天公将军张角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快下马投降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匹夫 敢冒充我威名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快跑啊 快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好汉 你又是何人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是周仓 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 字云长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 我终于亲眼见到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}壮士 壮士起来 快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关某受之不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 在下本是黄巾旧部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟张角征战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就听过将军的威名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你收下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 如能给你牵马拽镣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我死也甘心哪 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 我求求你 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我求求你了 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在此占山为王有多痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何必跟着我受罪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我所过的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天天危机四伏 凶险莫测
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓不怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要能做将军的一个步卒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胜过占山为王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我禀告二位嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她们允许了 我才敢收你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二位嫂嫂 关羽有事禀告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叔叔请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现有一壮汉 名叫周仓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他原本是黄巾旧部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现啸聚此山 做了这一山的寨主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他恳求于我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我收留他 做我的部属
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽不敢自专
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请二位嫂嫂决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这人先为贼 后为盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山寨中还有他不少强人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那留他只怕不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请叔叔斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂嫂说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂嫂认为你先从贼 后从盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寨中还有那么多的部卒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不肯留你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军哪 周仓事贼从盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是出于无奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想啊 天下这么恶浊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老实人活得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军你起兵之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不也杀过仇家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这山上还有很多的部卒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂嫂不肯留用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓立刻遣散所有部众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一把火烧了山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只身跟随将军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍候 容我再禀告二位嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀二位嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓情真意切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他愿烧掉山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遣散所有部众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只身一人跟随关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请二位嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果只是他一人 但随无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 起来 嫂嫂准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓此生此世 跟定将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓 前面是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前面五里就是古城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我原本想占那个城池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想两个月以前来了个恶盗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}霸占了城池 称王称霸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方圆三百里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有人敢惹他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连你也不敢惹他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那恶盗虎背熊腰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}穷凶极恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我连战他三次 都被他打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢不敢 帮我上前通关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有关将军在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是那恶盗的末日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这就给你通关去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令那厮滚出城来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙乾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你押车慢行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先去打开城关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再后接你们入城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命 将军千万小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卧牛山那贼首周仓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在城外喊话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫将军滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 请将军出城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手下败将 爷懒得睬他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但这次不止他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来了另外一个将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姓关名羽 字云长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错 正是将军的二哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军不是日夜寻找他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 他来得好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼盗 快快滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我关将军磕头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德 三弟 你怎么会在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 我是你二哥 是关羽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是恶贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有你这二哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何要杀我 说清楚不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我让你死个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来问你 你是否投降了曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是否被他拜将封侯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是否替他杀了颜良 文丑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼厮 你 你忘恩负义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还有脸来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看我不戳你一万个窟窿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之所以顺曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是为了保护嫂夫人 寻找兄长下落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是万般无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂夫人 嫂夫人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 你把曹军都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还敢狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}废话少说 你先吃我一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我斩了来将 以表忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我在这里三通鼓罢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就要斩了那贼将
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则 你就是忘恩负义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是个贼厮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 是你杀了我外甥秦琪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 是我关某所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要杀你抵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一通鼓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡阳 我本不想杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可你屡次辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我要取你首级洗我冤屈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二通鼓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽何人 永远不会忘恩负义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥 二哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下刚刚接报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说刘备二弟关云长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经离开曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一路上他过五关斩六将
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千里走单骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在已经到达了汝南郡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在一座古城中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其三弟张翼德相会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好哇 汝南距此不足二百里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这三两日内 他们就可以到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是他们兄弟相会以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却在古城停留不前 迁延观望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是为何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就得问问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们那生死与共的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀主公 左将军刘备拜会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫进来 喏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备拜见明公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 我刚刚听说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽离开曹操了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等他到了冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要将他斩首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为颜良 文丑报仇 以泄我恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}颜良 文丑如同二鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽如一虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公失二鹿而得一虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何恨之有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才只是戏言罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这么说是想试试你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实啊 我是非常喜爱关羽的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他们现在已经到了汝南古城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞也在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝南距此不远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么我们兄弟几日后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可以相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他们在古城停留不前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迁延观望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道这其中的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道关羽的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽因为杀了颜良 文丑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对我有愧 怕我治他的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才在古城停留不前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公明鉴 必然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽素来忠义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩颜良文丑之事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定然会让他寝食不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝南距此不到二百里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四日便可往返
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想派你亲自前往汝南
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}替我安抚关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后把关羽和张飞一同带来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们两人 我都要重用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下即刻选良马数匹 前往汝南
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四日之内 携二弟三弟回来拜见明公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧 早去早回 我静候佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这刘备此一去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕再也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备乃正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他既然答应了我 必不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不要以小人之心度君子之腹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公明鉴 倒是在下错怪他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 刘玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不快快下马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我许攸候你多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台有何见教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 我来问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你此一去汝南
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想必就再也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曾奉劝我家主公一定要留住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许兄为何相阻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这可是害我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 这不是明摆着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你若在此 你那生如手足的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 张飞势必前来相投
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然 你若离去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们三兄弟相聚后又何必再来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令许攸没有想到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这一片肺腑之言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公非但没有采纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反倒斥我是以小人之心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}度君子之腹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是何等的荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我许攸是小人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你刘备反倒成了正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公如此观人察事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再一次证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}证明他是一个昏君哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许兄啊 我在冀州客居半年多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早已感受到袁绍不能成大事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我如果继续留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非但一无所为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而会有性命之险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我必须离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才能履行天子诏命 举兵灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好一个举兵灭曹 刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就凭你现在这幅潦倒的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还敢与那奸贼曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}继续为敌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想 只要我还有一口气在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就会奋斗不止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我许攸送你一道建议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你如果采纳 我今天就放你走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当今天下 虽然尚未一统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但真正能与那曹操这奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相匹敌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可谓屈指可数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州刘表 雄踞荆襄之九郡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}财大气粗 兵精粮足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他才是曹操的真正大敌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只可惜我家主公袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与刘表素来不和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这刘表一直按兵未动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请玄德公你们三兄弟相会后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定共投刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必说服他举兵伐曹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许兄啊许兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不瞒你说 我早有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是我怕袁绍阻拦我不敢跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘景升跟我同属皇族后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我如劝他举兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他必会听从
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果真能够如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么在下许子远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天就当是为皇叔送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请吧 上马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢许兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明明知道袁绍并非英主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何 不如随我一块去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此言差矣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有道是 滴水之恩当涌泉相报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公虽然昏昧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可对我有知遇之恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经侍奉他十余年之久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我实在是不忍心弃他而去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许兄保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人各有志 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥 给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从这里到冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有一百多里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日日落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们定可与兄长相会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这越是快与大哥相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这心里越是不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 这是为何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄长在袁绍手下为幕僚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我却斩杀了他两员大将
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍岂能容我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错 这倒是个窘迫的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然这么着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥在城外三十里等候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先进城与兄长相会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺便看看袁绍的虚实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果无事 我回头来再接二哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为见兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我过五关斩六将 千里来寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在就快相见了 怕他作甚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}料那袁绍也不敢斩我人头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他才舍不得杀你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他还要用你为他建功哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓 这是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我探路探到前面的谷口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那里有座山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原本是没有驻军的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想从哪儿冒出来一个将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}引兵占住了山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是袁绍的部将
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不识得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那人也不答应 挥枪便刺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凶猛得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周仓孙乾 守护驿车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 我们前去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 走 孙乾接着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寨中何人 胆敢伤我部将
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快出来受死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长 冀德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙 真的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这真是苍天开眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从徐州兵败之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:23:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我苦苦寻找主公跟你们的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无奈之下 只有回到幽州
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}招募了公孙瓒的三千兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又回到此地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}继续寻找你们跟主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 子龙你可真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不光自己回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还带回来一支兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这比我在古城当县官可是强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这座山寨名叫关定庄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寨主与云长是同宗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也姓关 叫关定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人性情豪爽 为人高义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这三千兵马驻于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.18,0:24:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他不收分文
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.58,0:24:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且对两位兄长也是仰慕已久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}渴望见上一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走 咱们进山寨喝酒去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进庄 进庄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.13,0:24:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚生拜见各位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.17,0:24:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚生拜见各位前辈 晚生拜见各位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.20,0:24:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚生拜见各位前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.87,0:24:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军啊 老朽有个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知将军能否容纳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.95,0:24:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关老太爷有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想让他跟随将军外出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.88,0:25:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在将军的鞍前马后历练一番
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.72,0:25:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或许能博个功名
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.02,0:25:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回禀老太爷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.09,0:25:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下的日子过于凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.23,0:25:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一有个闪失 岂不饮恨终身
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.13,0:25:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不瞒将军说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从得知将军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.20,0:25:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关平已经求过我好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.04,0:25:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他定要跟随将军而去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.21,0:25:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军 你就收下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.95,0:25:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子啊 沙场征战 绝非儿戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.42,0:25:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这我知道 刀山火海绝无所惧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.63,0:25:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好志气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.60,0:25:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.23,0:25:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 你也没有子嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.50,0:25:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这关平英武过人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.47,0:25:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不如就把他收为义子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.04,0:25:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对啊 关将军 你就收他做个义子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.54,0:26:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我做不了主
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.21,0:26:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还得禀过兄长才成
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.25,0:26:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥啊 兄长不在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.58,0:26:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄弟说了也成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.69,0:26:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥 你暂且先收了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.32,0:26:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等和兄长相会之时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.36,0:26:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和子龙兄弟替你说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.09,0:26:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄长岂能不准
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.73,0:26:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}收了 收了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.67,0:26:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要我收你 可有三个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.57,0:26:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一是义气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.67,0:26:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人生在世 义气重于性命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.81,0:26:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二是胆气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.75,0:26:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论是做将还是做士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.78,0:26:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都要像项羽那样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}力拔山气盖世
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.46,0:26:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三是军规
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.46,0:26:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦从军 法不容情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀将军 我字字铭记
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.26,0:26:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我收下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.63,0:27:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢将军 孩儿叩见义父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.81,0:27:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.54,0:27:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.24,0:27:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来啊 各位共饮此杯 以谢苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.01,0:27:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.92,0:27:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.75,0:27:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀寨主
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.69,0:27:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外面有个叫糜芳的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.89,0:27:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前来求见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.82,0:27:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糜芳 快叫他进来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.09,0:27:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的天哪 你们都在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.40,0:27:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.37,0:27:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快说 兄长在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.90,0:27:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我先喘口气
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.64,0:27:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公听说你们在古城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.20,0:27:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天就已经离开了冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.14,0:27:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲与你们相会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.64,0:27:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公令我提前赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.21,0:27:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向你们报个信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.18,0:27:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公既然已经前往古城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就赶紧折道返回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老太爷 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.18,0:27:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告辞了 告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.40,0:28:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.51,0:28:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.21,0:28:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.61,0:28:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.91,0:28:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.19,0:29:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.43,0:29:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.21,0:29:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.51,0:29:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄弟想你想得好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.68,0:29:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大喜的日子 这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.46,0:29:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 大哥 起 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.90,0:29:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}账房 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶快 杀猪宰羊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.60,0:29:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在桃园摆酒相庆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.14,0:29:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就办 就办
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.99,0:30:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.89,0:30:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我三兄弟在涿郡桃园结义
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.43,0:30:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.13,0:30:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们四兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.56,0:30:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又在古城桃园相会
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.60,0:30:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此生此世 此情此景
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.67,0:30:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感慨万千
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.31,0:30:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.98,0:30:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这桃树怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.12,0:30:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么七零八落的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.05,0:30:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥 这都是小弟的错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.39,0:30:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这一听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.73,0:30:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥降了曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.09,0:30:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这气得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我 我都快气死了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.26,0:30:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我拿了根棍儿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.50,0:30:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把这桃园给打了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.17,0:30:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来年新春
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.81,0:31:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这桃树定会再发新枝
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.95,0:31:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这桃园就像我等兄弟的遭际
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然叠遭厄运 颠沛流离
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但最终定会否极泰来 再现繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.19,0:31:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 大哥说得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当饮一杯 来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.26,0:31:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.96,0:31:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干 来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.64,0:31:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那主公 日后有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.14,0:31:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是子龙心细
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.88,0:31:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早早就想下一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.08,0:31:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下一步嘛 我们要去荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.52,0:31:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.89,0:31:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.92,0:31:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 拜会荆州刺史刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.29,0:31:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}劝他与袁绍联手 举兵伐曹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我上表汉帝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.01,0:32:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他封我为大司马的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌已经回消息了 竟然不许
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.55,0:32:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操是看我在江东日渐强盛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.65,0:32:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才故意驳回我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.52,0:32:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.12,0:32:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨日防江将士截获一封
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.66,0:32:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吴郡太守许贡给曹操的密报
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.20,0:32:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}念
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.64,0:32:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.90,0:32:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策骁勇 堪与项羽比肩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.84,0:32:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷宜外示荣宠
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.98,0:32:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}召还京师 加以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.58,0:32:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可使其居外镇 以为后患
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.62,0:32:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大胆许贡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.15,0:32:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢勾结曹操谋害于我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.12,0:32:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.53,0:33:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许贡如若不除 必成大患
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.93,0:33:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你去 提他人头来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.67,0:33:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.05,0:33:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曲水流觞 叹如何
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.19,0:33:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人生如梦 易蹉跎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.12,0:33:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}金戈百万 尽在握
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.83,0:33:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饮罢回首 谁知我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.03,0:33:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是好诗 好诗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.80,0:33:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.21,0:33:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 出祸事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.57,0:33:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正高兴着哪 又有什么祸事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.14,0:33:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古城县令差人禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.98,0:33:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 关羽 张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.85,0:33:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在古城相会后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.42,0:33:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}集兵数千 往西而去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.89,0:34:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}往西 他难道不回冀州了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.06,0:34:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 你还指望刘备回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是投奔曹操去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.73,0:34:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.10,0:34:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曲水流觞 叹如何
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人生如梦 易蹉跎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.71,0:34:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这辙韵绝妙 好诗啊 好诗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.99,0:34:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.52,0:34:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.65,0:34:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备叛我 投奔曹操而去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.39,0:34:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非也 非也
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.53,0:34:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 依在下判断
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.63,0:34:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那刘备对曹操恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.63,0:34:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以说是不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.87,0:34:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}故在下可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.41,0:34:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘玄德绝不会投曹
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.98,0:34:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然他果真是西去了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.91,0:35:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那他一定是投了荆州的刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.62,0:35:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}试图以荆襄九郡为靠
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.39,0:35:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再图霸业
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.59,0:35:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道我还不如刘表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我对刘备是恩爱有加
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.30,0:35:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他却对我食言 背我 弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是他那个弟弟关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.61,0:35:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还杀了我的大将颜良 文丑
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如不将这三个贼兄弟斩首
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.99,0:35:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难消我心头的怒气
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.32,0:35:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图 我想刘备尚未走远
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.56,0:35:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你速派五千铁骑 星夜追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.40,0:35:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要拿住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可 不可
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.73,0:35:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公万万不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.47,0:35:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区一个刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.37,0:35:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}焉能成为吾之大敌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.41,0:36:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依在下之见
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.25,0:36:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒是那曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.88,0:36:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你一向明鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.72,0:36:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事你还要三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.52,0:36:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.19,0:36:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们当前的大敌是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.83,0:36:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而不是刘备 刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.50,0:36:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公明鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.54,0:36:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公圣明
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.94,0:36:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.94,0:36:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长公子袁谭
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.88,0:36:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率军十万从青州而来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二公子袁熙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.61,0:36:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率军十五万从幽州而来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三公子袁尚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.32,0:36:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率军十五万从并州而来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.35,0:36:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.32,0:36:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令所有文武
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.82,0:36:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日辰时 到帅府议兵
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.59,0:36:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.03,0:36:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有令
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.76,0:36:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传青州刺史袁谭
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.23,0:36:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幽州太守袁熙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并州上将袁尚进见
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.15,0:37:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿袁谭 儿袁熙 儿袁尚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.68,0:37:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.62,0:37:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.38,0:37:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿新练成的铁甲战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.09,0:37:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果排布开来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.59,0:37:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}犹如苍龙出海 猛虎下山
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.02,0:37:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下无人可敌
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.26,0:37:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 儿请命为先锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.63,0:37:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有谭儿的铁甲战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破曹军易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.27,0:37:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谭儿英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.21,0:37:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.08,0:37:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿新练成霹雳战车阵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.15,0:37:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦布展开来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.61,0:37:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定能山呼海啸 雷霆万钧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.45,0:37:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论何人军队想与之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.92,0:37:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眨眼间 定叫他灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请父王下令 儿愿做先锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.49,0:37:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有熙儿的霹雳战车阵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.76,0:38:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破曹操三军
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.43,0:38:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真如同滚滚雷霆击腐败落叶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}熙儿英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.28,0:38:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.98,0:38:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿所练得的箭弩阵
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.05,0:38:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}装备着新近打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.45,0:38:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五万副强弓硬弩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.68,0:38:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其每一支利箭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.08,0:38:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百步之内都能射胸腹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.55,0:38:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五十步之内
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.85,0:38:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能射透曹军的甲胄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.99,0:38:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据儿判断 父帅此次起兵灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.69,0:38:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其决战的战场必定设在官渡一带
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.60,0:38:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此 孩儿已经预先将兵器 军粮
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.77,0:38:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以及攻城所必须的军械
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.00,0:38:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部运往了距离官渡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.84,0:38:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几十里的乌巢镇
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.57,0:38:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.68,0:38:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为父帅的大军扎好了营盘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.51,0:38:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵马未动 粮草先行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.32,0:38:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尚儿年纪轻轻 却也是文武双全
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.39,0:38:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此乃大将之风范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.09,0:39:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.56,0:39:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿以为临敌制胜 须智勇双全
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.43,0:39:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿虽不才 但愿请为前锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿若不胜 请父帅将儿斩首正法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.97,0:39:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我儿英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子英雄盖世 盖世英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 儿愿为先锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.75,0:39:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿的铁甲战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 儿非做先锋大将不可
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.32,0:39:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如不胜 儿愿提头来见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 大哥二哥都是我的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.29,0:39:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身负大任
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.63,0:39:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但临敌接战 性命交关
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.63,0:39:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是请父帅让我为先锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.30,0:39:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沮授兄台
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.50,0:39:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三个公子 都在争做先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.94,0:39:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公为难了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.54,0:39:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公尚未立嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.11,0:39:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三个公子都在急做先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.64,0:39:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实 是在争大位
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.68,0:40:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么你估计
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.18,0:40:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公会立谁为先锋大将啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.89,0:40:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次和曹操决战事关重大
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.29,0:40:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先锋大将 我决定由
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.37,0:40:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由我袁绍亲自担当 这次灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.11,0:40:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公高明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.18,0:40:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你说 主公一旦贤明起来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.65,0:40:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是比天下任何主公都贤明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.95,0:40:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.36,0:40:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.49,0:40:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后日正午
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.30,0:40:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三军齐聚关前
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}举行灭曹操誓师大会
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.27,0:40:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祭天 祭地 祭祖 歃血出征
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.01,0:41:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
